commit.message:
Fix warning that argument is of incompatible pointer type

Cast the netstatus icon appropriately.

Prevent string from being copied out of bounds

The bound depends on the length of the destination argument,
not the length of the source argument.

Compile the --enable-gtk3 option with -Wno-deprecated-declarations

This is a GTK+ 2 application ported to GTK+ 3, not a native GTK+ 3
application. The deprecated GTK+ 3 features will most likely not be
removed and can still be used.

Add this compiler option so that only really important warnings are
issued.
Update German translation
Update language files
Update POT file
Add tooltips to explain how to define click and hotkey buttons
Update Portuguese translation
Update ChangeLog

Increase the size of the weather conditions icon in the panel

The icons provided by OpenWeatherMap occupy only a part (in the middle)
of the whole image area. When scaled down to panel size, they are barely
visible.

Cut off lines with no visible pixels at the top and bottom so that the
actual symbol remains larger after scaling.

Because cropping the image changes the aspect ratio, the new aspect
ratio must be saved and used when scaling the image.

Improve the image quality in the weather conditions dialog

In addition to the small icons, OpenWeatherMap provides images in four
times the size. So instead of scaling up the small icons for the weather
conditions dialog, which is only possible in modest quality, download
the larger images as well and scale these in better quality.

Add getImageFromURL() to the weather plugin for OpenWeatherMap

This is in preparation for loading a second image
in setImageIfDifferent().

Fix the wind direction display in the weather conditions dialog

Omit the wind direction if this information is not available
instead of displaying a "null pointer".

Arrange the weather conditions dialog information slightly differently

Display the conditions under the corresponding image and the temperature
below, separated by a blank line. Align everything centered.

This will make it easier to recognize the different information.

Add a comma before the temperature in the weather conditions tooltip

This will make it easier to recognize the different information.

Remove the blank line at the end of the weather conditions tooltip

This line is useless and makes the tooltip look weird.

Display the correct local time in the weather conditions dialog

In addition to the time zone, any daylight saving time must also
be taken into account.

Enable normal closing of the weather conditions dialog

The dialog can be closed with the escape key or the window's close
button now.

Do not display air pressure and visibility with decimal places

This precision is unnecessary and is not provided by the data.
Correct and complete the locale translation comments
Add missing locale translations for OpenWeatherMap
Update German translation
Update language files
Update POT file
Update copyright year

Add message contexts to some strings for better translations

Some languages require a string to have different translations.
Move ChangeLog entries to place them under the correct version
Update ChangeLog

Remove ambiguity in battery tooltip 

Minor change to replace "Current Voltage" to "Voltage now" to improve clarity

Show the dialog icon after the window has been presented

This fixes a bug that sometimes made the icon not appear where
it was supposed to, but in the upper left corner of the dialog
above the tab.
